1
00:00:02,920 --> 00:00:04,640
Ahhh!

2
00:00:04,640 --> 00:00:06,200
He looks so cool!

3
00:00:06,200 --> 00:00:07,920
It suits him perfectly!

4
00:00:07,920 --> 00:00:09,320
He has such an incredible presence!

5
00:00:14,180 --> 00:00:16,620
Kono Mizuki really is a handsome guy, isn't he?

6
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:19,700
How did I never notice that before?

7
00:00:20,300 --> 00:00:22,540
Actually, I also—

8
00:00:23,780 --> 00:00:25,500
am a handsome guy, you know!

9
00:00:29,780 --> 00:00:32,100
The prince who swore he would never marry...

10
00:00:32,100 --> 00:00:34,780
No! Put more emotion into it!

11
00:00:35,180 --> 00:00:37,500
More emotion...

12
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:38,940
It's just a play...

13
00:00:39,340 --> 00:00:40,980
You have to get into character.
Got it?

14
00:00:40,980 --> 00:00:41,980
Alright, let's go again.

15
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:47,700
The prince who swore he would never marry...

16
00:00:47,700 --> 00:00:49,980
falls in love at first sight with a girl he just met!

17
00:00:52,860 --> 00:00:53,860
That was completely wrong.

18
00:00:56,020 --> 00:00:57,540
He's such a terrible actor.

19
00:00:57,940 --> 00:00:58,940
Right?

20
00:00:59,020 --> 00:01:00,260
I think—

21
00:01:00,260 --> 00:01:01,940
I want to play Cinderella.

22
00:01:11,820 --> 00:01:13,100
Thanks.

23
00:01:13,780 --> 00:01:14,780
Huh?

24
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:18,020
I...

25
00:01:18,020 --> 00:01:20,180
I really wanted to enjoy my school life.

26
00:01:22,100 --> 00:01:23,220
But on my own,

27
00:01:24,580 --> 00:01:26,420
I just couldn't do it.

28
00:01:26,900 --> 00:01:28,180
Why are you being so formal?

29
00:01:30,540 --> 00:01:31,700
We're brothers, aren't we?

30
00:01:33,580 --> 00:01:34,580
Oh.

31
00:01:35,460 --> 00:01:36,740
You're right.

32
00:01:38,940 --> 00:01:39,940
Well then,

33
00:01:40,780 --> 00:01:42,300
I'm heading to the executive committee meeting.

34
00:01:56,380 --> 00:01:57,380
Iijima Hinata!

35
00:01:57,700 --> 00:01:59,260
Kono Mizuki said he's dropping out of the school festival.

36
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:00,860
What?
